metadata.name: [AI]·terror 001
metadata.description:
Horrific reality in Africa as mother's testimony reveals children being brainwashed & trained by rebels to kill their own families. Urgent calls for intervention to end child soldier recruitment & provide rehabilitation.

People are terrified of the potential of AI to surpass human intelligence and control, leading to potential harm for humanity, but the reality is that wars driven by humans are the ones will end with humanity.

#ClaireAIContest Rebuttal: AI will end humanity.


Concept, AI Curation & Digital Art by Mariela Di Nardo.
Dimensions 6000 x 4000 pixels.
